    <title>Manufacturing: Create and edit route task</title>
    <para>
    A "Routing Task" is an individual step or activity that is used in the manufacturing or assembling process of a 
    product.</para>
    <para>Examples include:</para>
    <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><para>Weighing out Raw Materials</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Assembling a Product</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Machining or Processing Materials</para></listitem>
   </itemizedlist>
    <para>
        In this screen you can create a new routing task and modify an existing Routing Task.
    </para>
